Package: distfitr
Type: Package
Title: Advanced Distribution Fitting with Enhanced Diagnostics
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-02-14
Authors@R: person("Ali", "Sadeghi Aghili", 
    email = "alisadeghiaghili@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Professional distribution fitting for R with comprehensive 
    goodness-of-fit tests, advanced diagnostics, bootstrap confidence intervals,
    and multilingual support. Provides enhanced functionality beyond fitdistrplus
    including multiple residual types, influence diagnostics, outlier detection,
    and parallel processing capabilities.
