    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    stats,
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    MASS,
    boot,
    parallel,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    fitdistrplus (>= 1.1-0),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0),
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    covr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
